## Graduation Boundary Map

Types that carry a [`GraduateToWasm4pm`][graduate] implementation are listed
here. The *Intake Surface* column names the `wasm4pm` entry point that accepts
this type once it leaves `wasm4pm-compat`.

> **Doctrine:** The product is CodeManufactory; RevOps is merely proof that
> CodeManufactory works.

[graduate]: crate::graduation::GraduateToWasm4pm

