### How to read this table

- **Rust Type** — the `wasm4pm-compat` structure type. It is structure-only here.
- **Source File** — where the type is defined in this crate.
- **Graduation Reason** — the [`GraduationReason`][reason] variant that motivated graduation. Hard signals (`NeedsConformanceExecution`, `NeedsReplay`, `NeedsObjectCentricQueryExecution`, `RebuildingProcessMiningLocally`, `NeedsDiscovery`) block release if unresolved. Soft signals (`NeedsBenchmarkGate`, `NeedsReceipts`) are advisory.
- **wasm4pm Intake Surface** — the `wasm4pm` crate entry point that consumes this type. Only valid after [`GraduationCandidate::is_grounded()`][grounded] returns `true`.

[reason]: crate::graduation::GraduationReason
[grounded]: crate::graduation::GraduationCandidate::is_grounded
